author: ryanleeschneider
content:
That would imply to me that all those multiple txs included the same blob, which is kind of odd tbh but as far as I know nothing prevents it.  Converting the blob to binary you can see that there's a content type header of PNG, so guessing this is NFT related:

```
00000000: 00b9 0002 6b63 6f6e 7465 6e74 5479 7065  ....kcontentType
00000010: 6969 6d61 6765 2f70 6e67 6763 6f6e 7465  iimage/pnggconte
00000020: 006e 745a 0001 c8aa 1f8b 0800 0000 0000  .ntZ............
```
